. Copulatory organs of 

Alopecosa krynickii

: 8 male palp, ventral; 9 bulbus, ventral-prolateral; 10 part of bulbus, retrolateral; 11–12 median apophysis, caudal and ventral; 13–14 embolic division, ventral and caudal-prolateral; 15 embolus, dorsal; 16–18 epigyne, ventral, dorsal, and dorsal-caudal. Abbreviations: 
